### Versioning System API Examples
### Use with REST Client extensions like VS Code REST Client

# Set base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api/v1
@contentType = application/json

### 1. Create Version Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/versioning/requests
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "input": {
    "content": "Artificial intelligence is transforming how businesses operate in the modern world. Machine learning algorithms are becoming increasingly sophisticated, enabling companies to automate complex processes and gain valuable insights from data.",
    "context": {
      "targetAudience": "business professionals",
      "purpose": "informative article",
      "keywords": ["AI", "machine learning", "business transformation"],
      "tone": "professional"
    }
  },
  "config": {
    "maxVersions": 3,
    "strategy": "sequential",
    "selectionCriteria": "quality",
    "improvementThreshold": 7,
    "enableComparison": true,
    "autoSelect": false,
    "retainAllVersions": true
  }
}

### 2. Generate Versions for Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/versioning/requests/REQUEST_ID/generate

### 3. Get Version Request Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/versioning/requests/REQUEST_ID

### 4. Get All Versions for Request
GET {{baseUrl}}/versioning/requests/REQUEST_ID/versions

### 5. Select Best Version
POST {{baseUrl}}/versioning/requests/REQUEST_ID/select-best
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "criteria": "quality"
}

### 6. Get Selected Version
GET {{baseUrl}}/versioning/requests/REQUEST_ID/selected

### 7. Compare Multiple Versions
POST {{baseUrl}}/versioning/requests/REQUEST_ID/compare
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "versionIds": ["VERSION_ID_1", "VERSION_ID_2", "VERSION_ID_3"],
  "criteria": ["quality", "content", "cost"]
}

### 8. Rank Versions by Criteria
POST {{baseUrl}}/versioning/requests/REQUEST_ID/rank
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "criteria": "quality"
}

### 9. Generate Improved Version
POST {{baseUrl}}/versioning/versions/VERSION_ID/improve
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "feedback": "The content needs better clarity and more specific examples. Add more depth to the analysis and improve the overall structure.",
  "context": {
    "targetAudience": "business professionals",
    "purpose": "informative article"
  }
}

### 10. Generate Variations
POST {{baseUrl}}/versioning/versions/VERSION_ID/variations
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "count": 2,
  "context": {
    "targetAudience": "technical executives",
    "purpose": "strategic insights"
  }
}

### 11. Add Feedback to Version
POST {{baseUrl}}/versioning/versions/VERSION_ID/feedback
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "versionId": "VERSION_ID",
  "type": "quality",
  "rating": 8,
  "comments": "Good overall quality but could use more specific examples",
  "suggestions": [
    "Add real-world case studies",
    "Include specific metrics and data",
    "Provide actionable recommendations"
  ],
  "timestamp": "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z"
}

### 12. Get Version Feedback
GET {{baseUrl}}/versioning/versions/VERSION_ID/feedback

### 13. Search Versions
GET {{baseUrl}}/versioning/versions/search?status=selected&minQualityScore=8&tags=improved

### 14. Get Versions by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/versioning/versions/status/generated

### 15. Update Version
PUT {{baseUrl}}/versioning/versions/VERSION_ID
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "selected",
  "qualityScore": 8.5,
  "metadata": {
    "tags": ["selected", "high_quality"]
  }
}

### 16. Select Specific Version
POST {{baseUrl}}/versioning/requests/REQUEST_ID/versions/VERSION_ID/select

### 17. Reject Version
POST {{baseUrl}}/versioning/requests/REQUEST_ID/versions/VERSION_ID/reject

### 18. Run Improvement Loop
POST {{baseUrl}}/versioning/requests/REQUEST_ID/improve
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "maxIterations": 3,
  "targetQuality": 8.5
}

### 19. Get Version Metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/versioning/requests/REQUEST_ID/metrics

### 20. Get System Metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/versioning/metrics

### 21. Quick Version Generation - YouTube Script
POST {{baseUrl}}/versioning/youtube-script
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "AI is changing how we create content for YouTube. Let me tell you about the latest tools and techniques that can help you grow your channel.",
  "config": {
    "maxVersions": 4,
    "enableImprovementLoop": true,
    "targetQuality": 8.0
  }
}

### 22. Quick Version Generation - SEO Article
POST {{baseUrl}}/versioning/seo-article
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "Search engine optimization is crucial for online visibility. This guide covers the most important SEO strategies for 2024.",
  "config": {
    "maxVersions": 3,
    "strategy": "improvement",
    "targetQuality": 8.5
  }
}

